summary: This is an email chain from December 18, 2019, discussing a meeting with a female witness. The participants note the meeting was less productive than hoped, as the witness's recollections about Ghislaine Maxwell are significantly less detailed than her recollections about Jeffrey Epstein.

events.title: Meeting with a witness
events.description: A meeting was held with a female witness. The content suggests the witness was being interviewed about her recollections of Jeffrey Epstein and Ghislaine Maxwell.

keyFacts: A meeting with a witness took place on or around December 17, 2019.
The meeting was described as 'not as productive as hoped or anticipated'.
The witness's recollections about Ghislaine Maxwell were 'significantly less than what she recalls about Epstein in relevant ways'.
The email chain involves coordination for a follow-up discussion among the participants.
All personal names and email addresses in the document are redacted.
